snippet.title: Waltair Veerayya Theatrical Trailer | Megastar Chiranjeevi | Ravi Teja | Shruti Haasan | Bobby | DSP
snippet.description:
Waltair Veerayya Theatrical Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers. Waltair Veerayya is an upcoming Telugu film ft. Megastar Chiranjeevi, Ravi Teja, Shruti Haasan and Catherine Tresa. Music composed by Rockstar Devi Sri Prasad. Story, Dialogues & Direction by KS Ravindra (Bobby Kolli). Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y Ravi Shankar under the banner Mythri Movie Makers, Audio On Sony Music.

Waltair Veerayya Grand Release on 13th January, 2023.

snippet.title: Veera Simha Reddy Trailer | Nandamuri Balakrishna | Gopichand Malineni | Thaman S | Shruti Haasan
snippet.description:
Veera Simha Reddy Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers. Presenting our NATASIMHAM Nandamuri Balakrishna, Shruti Haasan and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in Veera Simha Reddy. The film has been Written and Directed by Gopichand Malineni. Music composed by Thaman S. Cinematography helmed by Rishi Punjabi. Dialogues Penned by Sai Madhav Burra and Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y Ravi Shankar, under the banner Mythri Movie Makers.

Veera Simha Reddy Grand Release on 12th January, 2023.

snippet.title: Mystery of Flight IC-814 | The Worst Plane Hijacking in Indian History | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
In the year 1999, Indian Airlines Flight IC-814 was traveling from Kathmandu to Delhi. It was carrying 180 passengers who went on to live the worst nightmare of their lives. This is their story. This hijack is considered the worst Airplane Hijack ever in Indian history. For more than 7 days the plane flew from one location to another, from Lahore to Dubai and then to Afghanistan. See how the events unfolded and how the former Indian govt under Atal Bihari Vajpayee managed the situation.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 04 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 04 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song | Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare | Ajaneesh Loknath |Nithin Krishnamurthy
snippet.description:
Kantara music director B. Ajaneesh Loknath comes with another magical creation in Nithin Krishnamurthy's directorial debut, Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare. The first single "Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song" sung by the Music director himself and penned by Yogarajbhat Fans is an another attraction for the film. Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare is a one-of-a-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy's hostel, featuring 500 new talents and cameo by superstars, Rishab Shetty, Ramya, Pavan Kumar & Shine Shetty.  The film is made under the Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. The director who has also served as one of the four producers of the film along with Prajwal B.P., Varun Kumar, and Arvind S. Kashyap, who is handling cinematography as well and Presented by Paramvah Pictures.

Listen to the song on all your favorite Music platforms : https://bfan.link/hostel-hudugaru-protest-song

https://bit.ly/SubscribeToA2Music for more !

snippet.title: Team CID का एक अतरंगी Sting Operation | CID | Sony Pal Rewind
snippet.description:
CID officers have changed their avatars which includes Senior Officer Daya, Shreya, Purvi and Pankaj and are undercover to bust a strange and mysterious racket. Let's see what this case is all about. Stay tuned for more. Watch now.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast: Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastav, Dayanand Shetty, Dinesh Phadnis, Narendra Gupta, Shraddha Musale, Hrishikesh Pandey, Ansha Sayed, Abhay Shukla, Ajay Nagrath, Janvi Chheda
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#cid2023 #सीआईडी #sonypal 

Click here to Subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1siG-BtePnttdEXHWlLV3v

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all episodes of CID:  
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0ELExJn9rGFzmk9yXaviyk

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 4th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa Cosmetics

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Having visions of his past, Bihaan wakes up traumatised and consumes some pills. Sankar then reveals that those pills will help erase all memories of Thapki and make him forget her. But, will that happen?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: सिर्फ 1बार हलवाई के 3ट्रिक से तिलगुड़ लाडू बनएंगे तो न कड़क होंगे 1दम खस्ता| Original Til Gud ke Ladoo
snippet.description:
#tilgudladoorecipe Til ke laddu or sesame ladoos are traditional Indian sweet balls made with sesame seeds, jaggery and cardamom powder. Til ke Laddu Recipe is a nutty, tasty, ladoo made with sesame seeds, jaggery, peanuts. Sesame laddu is a good warming winter sweet snack. Til ke laddu are high in magnesium which means they are good for the heart by lowering the blood pressure. Tilkut Recipe Til Gur Ladoo Recipe Dishes prepared from Til(sesame seeds) provide heat and energy to the body which are both necessary to beat the cold. Til Ladoo is delightfully nutty, naturally sweetened with jaggery, and protein-packed. This recipe makes the Til Gud Ke Laddu in a food processor or blender without making the jaggery syrup.

snippet.description:
►Click here to Subscribe *Star Bharat* : https://www.youtube.com/c/StarBharat
►Watch More Like This https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCy2rLnGdwoJcSAtixNdsPQ



►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

snippet.title: Radhakrishn || Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 252 || Dwarka par aane wala hai sankat
snippet.description:
►Click here to Subscribe *Star Bharat* : https://www.youtube.com/c/StarBharat
►Watch More Like This https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCy2rLnGdwoJcSAtixNdsPQ



►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: क्या अलग हो जाएंगे Bihaan और Tina? | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 587
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Shraddha tries to convince the Pandey family to send Tina away to a boarding school. But Bihaan and Dhruv are against this decision. Will Shraddha be able to change their minds? Meanwhile Thapki receives a distressing call from Bani's school.

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Watch more videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX18mvVSh-bzmIBfH3sKcKbGZQJ_OGGIg

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3662 - 7 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3662: Jetha: The Kind One
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha is melancholy after Bawri's decision to cut all ties. Bagha is taken back to Gada Electronics by Sodhi. Everyone tries to cheer Bagha up, but he seems traumatized. Nattu Kaka assigns him some work to keep his mind off Bawri, but Bagha commits a massive mistake in his work. Bagha's kind-hearted boss, Jethalal, tells Nattu Kaka to take care of Bagha while taking care of the shop. Nattu Kaka takes Bagha to their house and consoles him by talking about their village, but Bagha gets sad. How will Nattu Kaka handle Bagha and his emotions?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3662, 7 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000203615

snippet.description:

Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 249 |Rukmini hain Radha ka hi roop | Radhakrishn  राधाकृष्ण

►Click here to Subscribe *Star Bharat* : https://www.youtube.com/c/StarBharat
►Watch More Like This https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCy2rLnGdwoJcSAtixNdsPQ
►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: मैंने जबसे इस तरीके से पाव भाजी है बनाया तबसे सरे पुराने तरीको को बेकार पाया | Instant Pav Bhaji
snippet.description:
#pavbhaji #mumbaistyle #bhaji 

INGREIDENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

2 Onions (Slices)
3 Desi Tomatoes 
1 Capsicum
1 Whole Garlic 
2 Inch Ginger 
2 - 3 Tbsp Butter 
Oil As Needed 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder 
1 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
1 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 Beatroot 
1 - 2 Carrot 
1 Cup Peas
3 Potatoes 
250 - 300 Gms Cauli Flower 
1.5 Cups Water 
4 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Bleck Pepper Powder 
2 Tbsp Kasuri Methi 
 Coriander Leaves 

FOR TADKA 

3 - 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped )
1 Onion (Finely Chopped )
2 Tbsp Pav Bhaji Masala 

FOR PAV 

2 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Poav Bhaji Masala 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
Coriander Leaves.

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

*About* 
------------

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3661 - 6 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3661: A Heart-Broken Bagha!
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bawri does not arrive at Lovely Garden, Bagha goes to her apartment. Bagha is greeted by her neighbor as Bawri's fiancée, but she informs Bagha that Bawri has urgently left her place. Bagha reluctantly exits her apartment. A few moments later, Bagha receives a text message from Bawri in which she states that she will never speak to him again. Bagha is devastated, and Sodhi discovers him crossing the street erratically. What made Bawri decide to cut all ties with Bagha?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3661, 6 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Officer Purvi Risks Her Life To Stop A Car | CID | Hidden In A Car | 07-01-2023
snippet.description:
A man is traveling with his wife and due to something unpredictable they hit a truck and lose their life. Team CID starts their investigation and they are unable to find the reasons behind the accident. As the case gets more and more complicated, how will Team CID solve this case? Watch the full episode to find out! 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: -914
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #cid2023 #newcid #crime #latestcid 

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all the action-packed episodes of CID:  
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIVl_1hRA4uY9pm9ceOJ8BYl

Shraddha and Sankar have done almost everything to get control of the Pandey house. The seven-year-old shocking evil plan is about to be revealed. Will anyone ever know about their evil deeds?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 05 Teaser - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 05 Teaser - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3661 - Bawri Ne Kiya Bagha Se Breakup?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
